Package: datr
Title: Dat Protocol Interface
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Hartgerink", , "chris@libscie.org", c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The datr package provides R users with a way to interface with 
    the Dat p2p network. Currently, the package allows you to clone Dat archives
    from the network, share your own files, and install an R package from a Dat.
License: GPL-3
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1)
Imports: 
    devtools,
    rjson,
Suggests: 
    covr,
    testthat
ByteCompile: true
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
